To prove the injectivity of the map `chineseMap : (R ÔžŞ ÔĘů i, I i) Ôćĺ+* ╬á i, R ÔžŞ I i`, we need to show that if two elements in `R ÔžŞ ÔĘů i, I i` are mapped to the same element in `╬á i, R ÔžŞ I i`, then they must be the same element in `R ÔžŞ ÔĘů i, I i`.

