`Quotient.mk I x` is the coset of `x` modulo `I`.
`Quotient.mk I x = Quotient.mk I y` means the cosets of `x` and `y` are equal.
The definition of equality of cosets is `x - y Ôłł I`.
So `h1 i` directly gives `x - y Ôłł I i`.
Since this holds for all `i`, `x - y Ôłł I`.
So `x = y`.

